  <Section Title="Declaration">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[struct ApiVersion;]]></Code>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ApiVersion</TypeRef> structure stores the major and minor version of the graphics API targeted by a renderer plugin.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      The default constructor initializes both fields to zero. The two-argument constructor initializes both fields explicitly.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Members">
    <DataMemberList>
      <DataMemberListEntry Visibility="Public" Type="uint32_t" Name="major">
        The major API version number.
      </DataMemberListEntry>
      <DataMemberListEntry Visibility="Public" Type="uint32_t" Name="minor">
        The minor API version number.
      </DataMemberListEntry>
    </DataMemberList>
  </Section>
